          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1629301966574-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop the <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into chips</p><p>Add the <strong>chips</strong> to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 30 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1629301978158-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
