            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Top the sausage meat evenly with the <strong>caramelised onion</strong> (save the pan!)</p><p>Brush a little <strong>cold water </strong>around the edges of the pastry</p><p>Fold the pastry over the mixture and press it together with your fingers to seal in the sausage & onion with as little air trapped inside as possible</p><p>Crimp the seal edges with a fork – these are your <strong>sausage rolls</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
