        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>sausage rolls</strong> with the <strong>grated cheese </strong>and sprinkle over the <strong>nigella seeds</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 15-20 min or until the sausage is cooked through and the pastry is puffed up and golden</p>",
