    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil half a kettle</p><p>Heat a medium pot with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once melted, add 1/2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1 tbsp]</span><strong> flour</strong> and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Add the <strong>chicken stock mix</strong> and 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and cook for 8-10 min or until thickened – this is your <strong>gravy</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
