    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, rip the leaves off the <strong>spring greens</strong>, discard the tough stalks, then layer the leaves over each other, roll them up and slice into thin strips</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> spring greens</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until tender with a bite</p>",
